content.description: This job reads data from ACX Guidewire DB and loads it into the Metal staging tables. It follows a one-to-one mapping with no transformations.
content.name: cdi_map_acx_ea_assessment_summary_metal_load

object.customQuery:
select
a.SystemId,
a.ParentId,
a.CMMContainer,
a.Id,
a.assessmentId,
a.solutionId,
a.solutionName,
a.businessFunction,
a.assessedEntity,
a.category,
a.score,
a.scorePercentile,
a.normalizedScore,
a.recommendedActionDescription,
a.recommendedActionCode,
a.conclusionDescription,
a.conclusionCode,
a.scoreDate,
a.assesmentDetail,
a.error,
a.RowId                     
from
eaassessmentsummary a
inner join advrxxchangedbeans b
on
a.Systemid = b.Systemid
and a.CmmContainer = b.CmmContainer
and b.CmmContainer = 'DataReport'
WHERE 
CONCAT(b.adddt, ' ', substr(b.addtm, 1, 8))>= $LASTRUNTIME;
